name: BetaPro S&P 500 Daily Inverse ETF
longDescription: SPXI seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to one times (100 percent) the inverse (opposite) of the daily performance of the S and P 500 R. SPXI does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
